When using Edge on Android all the charts give an error and are not shown.

All the .js files on /static/dsmr_frontend/js/dsmr-reader/live/*.js are not shown because of "chart_object**?**.resize();"

E.g. in electricity.js
This 
```
$(window).resize(function () {
    echarts_electricity_graph?.resize();
});
```

should be:

```
$(window).resize(function () {
    echarts_electricity_graph.resize();
});
```
